{"tid":2110362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"羅拔臣：向阿仙奴展示冠軍氣勢","createTime":"2020-07-16T00:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T10:09:04.000Z","uid":72497,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36534b41463c6c38a6d0922b68cf051e1cf2ce4e","tid":2110362,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"英超冠軍利物浦周三作客阿仙奴前，左閘羅拔臣揚言：「我們要踢出冠軍級表現。」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦上輪與般尼言和1:1，今季主場首次失分，如想爭取突破100分大關，今番面對阿仙奴非勝不可。「兵工廠在打吡戰敗北，一定很想反彈，但我們明顯地要拿出冠軍級表現，證明我們是英超冠軍，並以帶走3分為目標。」紅軍左閘羅拔臣（Andy Robertson）表示。 「當然，己隊預期會是一場惡戰，畢竟他們要為歐洲賽席位而戰，相信兩隊都想贏，希望贏的是我們。」<br />\n<br />\n上場取得今季第2球的羅拔臣續說：「最後3場不易應付，我們期待挑戰，盡可能全取所有分數。」 由於夏天休季時間減少，這位蘇格蘭國腳認為紅軍季尾不能放鬆，以免影響下季的氣勢。"},{"pid":"48e83f37fdc42557787cc8eadf98766ef08c04c7","tid":2110362,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:56:17.000Z","msg":"飲大咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f127f7771f5f791abfcf7793e63e1fe78d9c8a35","tid":2110362,"uid":72497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"48e83f37fdc42557787cc8eadf98766ef08c04c7","tid":2110362,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:56:17.000Z","msg":"飲大咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSaJPHS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSaJPHS.png&h=ef476959&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8a5541a6d8b958f1fc92ad60e342f3333863cee","tid":2110362,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"佢有肋攻喎"},{"pid":"1eb26a4d26d0b759c059bb50beee330538e453a6","tid":2110362,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8a5541a6d8b958f1fc92ad60e342f3333863cee","tid":2110362,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"佢有肋攻喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:06:00.00